unittitle_ssm: Bella C. Landauer Collection of Business and Advertising Ephemera
abstract_ssm: Collection of mainly 19th and 20th century advertising ephemera. Formats in the collection include American trade cards, lottery tickets, handbills, labels, broadsides, calendars, billheads, price lists, advertising fans, and other materials of history and popular culture. Media range from rough woodcuts to chromolithographs.
